text: Kenji Eto (born 22 January 1948) is a Japanese equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1976 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1948 births Category:Living people Category:Japanese male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Japan Category:Equestrians at the 1976 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
